Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:11.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人は　今　１分１秒を惜しんで 修行しているからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:11.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Th-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}また会おうと伝えてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you not call for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ではな。 それじゃあね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And here... You're covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカを　よろしく頼む。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is this creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:27.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつは冷静に見えて　無鉄砲。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:27.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What do I want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:33.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}頭がいいのに 考えなしのとこがある。 見たところ　あんたには 心を開いてるみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:33.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the northeast elevator down to the \Nbasement, to search for Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありがとうございました！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you find her, escape without us. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッ　あの野郎 本気で全部　買う気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the King and his three Royal Guards \Nare in the throne room, we proceed with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こっちの予算も 完全に読まれているし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The problem is, what if they're not there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残り１個…　クソっ！ 必ず落としてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're really hung up on that... What are the chances of that happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「また会えるし 今は修行　頑張れ」ってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it's highly unlikely. But the unusual happens pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}え　よかったのに　そんなの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Aren't you contradicting yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:17.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカが ヨークシンを出るなら安心だって 喜んでたじゃねえかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:17.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We researched the enemy's behavior extensively \Nbefore deciding on a day for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:25.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そりゃそうだけど 黙って行っちゃうなんて…。 ほれっ！ ゼパイルからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:25.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you're waiting for someone to be \Nin a certain place, at a certain time, that's typically when the unexpected happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつも 「また会おう」って言ってたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In my old job, I saw this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:34.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ!?　ゼパイルさんも？ ああ　約束通り きっちり１億に戻してくれてな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:34.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The unusual always happens \Non the day you've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:39.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホントだ。 これで質に入れた ハンターライセンスを取り戻せるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:39.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In my old job, I could wait for the next chance, to ensure my success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:43.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　やっぱり　すごい人だね ゼパイルさんって。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:43.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But this time, that isn't an option. We can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンターライセンスってやつは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So we should take time now to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}質屋が即金で １億出すってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}how we'll act in different situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっと　しかるべきとこで売ったら 桁２つは違うんじゃねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even if they aren't in the throne room, \Nif they're still in the palace, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:08.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ！ そうだ！ 俺もプロハンターになって ライセンス売りゃあ　いいんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:08.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou's En is enough to cover the palace and \Nits surrounding courtyards, and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:15.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうすりゃあ　おめぇ 借金どころか　一気に利子生活！ よっしゃ！　そうと決まれば 善は急げだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:15.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if we sense that creepy aura when we enter, we'll know that they're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:25.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンター試験の準備　準備！ １６番　６０２億で 『グリードアイランド』落札！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:25.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}From there, we just follow that \Nsinister aura to where it feels densest, and they'll be at its center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありがとうございました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The question is what we do if \Nwe don't sense Pitou's aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}６０２億だとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In other words, what we do \Nif they aren't in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:35.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すげぇな　結局　７本とも 全部　落札しちまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:35.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or if they're in the palace, \Nbut they aren't using En.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:40.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その代わり　個人資産の 半分を失ったそうだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:40.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Would they be in the palace, but not using En to guard the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:47.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　先日　３０５億で落札した 『グリードアイランド』を 何者かに強奪された バッテラ氏でしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:47.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what happened when \NKnov-san infiltrated the palace! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}めげることなく　昨日は２７８億
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, that's what I can't make sense of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:54.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今日は　なんと６０２億ジェニーで 落札いたしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:54.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}According to Colt, Knov saw Pouf's aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:59.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フンっ！ [TV]　そこまでするのには 何か理由があるんでしょうかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:59.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard never leaves the King's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　ゲームクリア後に　隠し財宝が 示された地図が出るとか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if Pouf was there, the other two were \Nalso in the palace with the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:12.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}巨大な龍が現れて 願いごとを １つ叶えてくれるとか まことしやかな噂が 飛び交ってますがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:12.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, why did Pitou stop \Nusing the puppets and En, leaving Pouf to handle security, which allowed Knov to infiltrate the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まいどあり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe the reason has to do with \Nhow Pitou's power works...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}帰ろ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we should ask Colt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結局　全ての『グリードアイランド』を 競り落とした　バッテラ氏！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd guess that during that time, \NPitou was healing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼は同時に　プレーヤーを 募集しておりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:33.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}期日は今日！ 会場前は　すでに 長蛇の列になっております。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:33.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I told you that Pitou was the \None who restored Kite, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お待たせいたしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thinking back, I don't believe Pitou \Nused En during that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これより　プレーヤー選考会を 始めたいと思います。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thus, healing must require a \Ngreat deal of concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:47.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すでに　ご承知の通り このゲームに参加するには 念能力が不可欠！ そこで審査の方法ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:47.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So while healing someone, Pitou cannot use En or the puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず　おのおのの 「念」を見せていただき
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我々が　独断で合否を決定する …という方法を とらせていただきます。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means that someone, most likely the King or one of the \NRoyal Guard, was injured and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}審査を担当いたしますのは プロハンター　ツェズゲラ氏です。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}required healing, so the En \Nand puppets disappeared. But hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マネーハンター　ツェズゲラ！ 奴が動いてるってことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who would have been able to \Ninjure one of those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲーム 見返りもデカいってことだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}True... An internal dispute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　早速　審査に入る。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Maybe the King injured one of the Royal Guard? No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１人ずつ　ステージの上で 「練」を見せてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is no chance that Pitou \Nwould endanger the King
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ステージは シャッターとカーテンで仕切り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}by removing that En to heal someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他の者には　様子が 分からないように配慮する。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３２名　合格者が出た時点で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means that the one injured... ...was the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}審査は終了とする。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see... What you're saying makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:36.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　審査を受ける方は こちらから　どうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:36.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But then the bigger question \Nis who injured the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}説明は　あれだけかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yep, so our conclusion was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは　１番目の方　どうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King injured himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:07:01.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最低限の説明 分からないことだらけ でも　周りの奴らは 当然のように行動している
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:07:01.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Under what circumstances \Nwould that have happened? We don't know why, but it's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:08.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつらは分かってるんだ こちらの問いに対し 決して返答などないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:08.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll admit that I didn't question our \Nsudden stroke of luck too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達がすべきこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that chance was only possible \Nunder abnormal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:15.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　説明されたことから 残りを推察し　最善を尽くすこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:15.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are they starting to lose control?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:24.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　この行動の選択も含めて 過程は全て審査の一部 会場には　約２００人の志願者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:24.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That isn't good... I'm starting to think something's \Ngoing on inside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１００人近くが列をつくり 審査待ち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We will now begin moving to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:36.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その周りを ５０人以上が取り囲み 機をうかがっている そして　２０人ほどは動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:36.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Citizens of sector A-1, assemble in \NDiego Plaza at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:42.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どのグループの判断が 正しい？ 次の方　どうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:42.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The citizens of the other sectors \Nshould prepare to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おかしい…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, they're starting to file out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すでに　１０人近くが 中に入ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They've begun their march...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰一人　出て来ない 入った奴ら 全員　合格したってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ten hours until midnight, when the selection starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:06.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マズいぞ… 俺達も並ぶべきか？ てんで話にならない。 ん？ え？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:06.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In twenty-five hours, tomorrow afternoon at three, five million humans will fill the palace grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:11.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今　並んでる連中と その周りを取り囲んでる連中さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:11.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Has the situation in Peijing changed? I thought it was only one skilled enemy, \Nbut now there are a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}特に行列の周りで ウロウロしてる奴ら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:15.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So there are reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:20.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさか　不合格者が 戻って来るのを期待して 中の様子を聞く気かねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:20.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They may try to use the celebration \Nas cover to approach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:25.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちゃんと下調べが済んでいて 普通に頭を働かせれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:25.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then the danger will be greatest \Nduring the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:29.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}順番を競って 並ぶ意味など　ないことに 気づきそうなもんだが。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:29.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, since the King will be \Nparticipating in the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((つまり　新たなプレーヤーを 投入できないのだよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our greatest concern is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((だから 新たなプレーヤーは厳選する))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the King somehow being taken beyond our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:50.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか！　この選考会では ３２名も合格者は出ない。 その通り。 １０年以上も　クリアした者が いないとされるゲーム。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:50.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Assuming that they have a Nen \Nuser capable of translocation, and that that person can use the ability \Nto isolate the King somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:55.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかも　前のプレーヤーが 生きてる限り 後の者は参加できない仕組み。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:55.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That means at least one of us must stay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ならば　保険の意味でも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}by the King's side during the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}より有望な挑戦者が 現れた時に備えて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:05.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いくつか空席を残しておこうって 考えるのが普通。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:05.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As it is, he's been upset by how \Nclose we've stayed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今回の審査で選ばれるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we guard him secretly, \Nwithout his knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく２０人ちょっと ってとこだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We need someone to stay just close \Nenough to monitor his surroundings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:17.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今　並んでる連中と　その周りで たむろしてる奴らは 俺が見ても明らかにダメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:17.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}while still carrying out his own role in the selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:26.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見込みがあるのは　開始と同時に 迷わず席を立った数人と からくりを理解して席に残り 集中してる俺達。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:26.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whose size won't attract attention, who won't get absorbed in an amusing task...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぁ？　そっちの坊ず。 あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Very well, I am the best choice for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン…　お前　気づいてたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Strictly by process of elimination, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:37.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　何となくだけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:37.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:41.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}主催者側から考えたら せっかく集めた人達の実力は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:41.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their presences have completely disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全員　確かめておきたいって 思うのが人情かなって。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't sense any residual aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:54.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アハハ…　そりゃそうだ 坊ず　おめぇの勝ち！ いや　大したもんだよ 自分のことわりを持って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:54.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They must be using Zetsu to hide \Namong the marching humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:10:00.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに身を委ねるってのは なかなか　できねえんだ。 正解への道が　険しく危ないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:10:00.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカと利口の両方を 兼ね備えてねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}前へ進めなくなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Around a hundred per building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次の方　どうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They must have been packed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:14.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の名はプーハット まっ　よろしくな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:14.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then if we conceal our presences, they can only assume that we're \Nhiding among the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああいう うんちく　たれんのに限って 落ちたりすんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Maybe they'll cancel the march?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プハ…。 聞こえるよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　確かに あいつの言う通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That would mean delaying or \Neven canceling the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　最善の手にこだわって 理屈で考え過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which would imply the King had \Naccepted defeat and compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先に行くぜ。 うん！　頑張って。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard won't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:37.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}冒険しなきゃ　前に進めない それだけ危険な道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:37.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The celebration will begin as scheduled, \Nno matter the cost. Tomorrow morning, at 3 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:48.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((１００％やれると 確信した時だけ実行し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:48.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once the humans began to move, my puppets could no longer tell them apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それ以外は待て))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I recall them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:57.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((俺達の最も重要な仕事は 待つこと)) ((勝算もなしに 自分の能力を見せるなど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:57.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, giving the enemy free \Nrein would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最も愚かな行為だぞ)) それは　親父の理屈… 俺は　もう殺し屋じゃ　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Have the puppets join the soldiers that \Nare guiding the citizens, as a deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:25.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの時の「練」が　実力の 全てではないことを見せてくれ。 じゃ　行くぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:25.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}'Sup? As expected, the puppets have joined the march.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オーラを電気に!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are six entrances to the \Nrooms that lead to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:47.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理論上は確かに可能 …が　あり得ん！ ゼロから　この４日間で 覚えたなどということは… どう？　もう少し見るかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:47.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll avoid the entrances in front of the \Npalace, where security will be tighter, and wait by entrances A, B, \Nand C, behind the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:57.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　よかろう…　合格だ。 うしっ！ しかし　一朝一夕で 身につくことじゃ　ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:57.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once we've entered the rooms, the only exit will lead inside the palace. What? You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}拷問に近い強力な電気を 浴びる修行だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't be absurd. I merely want to be sure we're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:06.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}数年はいるはず　お前は一体…。 強力な電気ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:06.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Waiting by the entrances involves \Nquite a lot of risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:11.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生まれた時から浴びてたぜ 家庭の事情でね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:11.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if we enter the rooms too early, \Nwe won't be able to exit until midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}７人か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And we can't use cell phones near the palace, since the Ants will pick up on the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:32.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり　おっさんの読み通り 受かってるのは 真っ先に動いた奴らと 席で待ってた奴ら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:32.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I think it's dangerous to spend hours \Nwaiting inside the rooms, not knowing if there have been \Naccidents or changes in the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さて　ゴンは大丈夫かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you're the one who said it was \Nrisky to wait outside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:51.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン！ あっ！　キルア！ よかった！　選ばれたんだね！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:51.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm the only one who can freely \Nenter and exit these rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}当然よ！　今の音　お前か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If anything happens, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For now, you should rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:02.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まったく… 末恐ろしい子供達だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:02.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will you be okay? I shouldn't have any problem \Ninvestigating the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:12.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さて　とりあえず おめでとうと言っておこう。 君達２１人には　『グリードアイランド』を プレーする権利を与える。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:12.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even if I'm right beside the palace, as long \Nas I'm out of range of Pitou's En...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームをクリアした場合の報酬は ５００億ジェニー。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}詳細は　契約書に書いてあるので
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou doesn't use a standard circular En.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:24.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}夕方５時の出発まで よく目を通し サインを済ませておくように。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:24.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It changes shape like an amoeba, \Ngiving it extended range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カンパイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what Kite came in contact with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とりあえず　第１関門　突破だな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And it was probably deliberate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:35.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これ ちょっと見てほしいんだけど。 何だ？　契約書か。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:35.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a fighter's instinct to want to know \Nhow strong the opponent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:43.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}要約すると３つだな。 １つ　ケガをしたり 死んだりしても文句言わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:43.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And his instinct led him to misjudge their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つ ゲーム内から持ち帰った物は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In some areas, that En can \Nstretch two kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全て　バッテラ氏に所有権がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Make sure you stay out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３つ　ゲームをクリアした者には
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５００億ジェニーの報酬を与える。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In this room, I'm the one who most fears them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}特に　問題は　ねえだろ。 うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't do anything crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:01.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃ　サインして終わりだな。 大事なのは　２つ目だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:01.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:08.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームの中から 現実に持ち帰って来る何か。 奴が　大枚はたいて求めてるのは その何かだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:08.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We will now head to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「何か」って　何だ？ 何だって渡すよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Any person who leaves their line \Nwill be shot on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が欲しいのは　物じゃ　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあな。 レオリオ　試験　頑張ってね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.52,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次　会う時は　お医者さんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.52,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You knew that Komugi was being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おめぇ　そりゃ最短でも ４年　会わねえってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, I was monitoring the area with En.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　もっと早く ゲームクリアするつもりだけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, I determined that there was no threat \Nto Your Majesty, so I ignored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フンっ　負けねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}From now on, monitor Komugi's surroundings, and deal with any threats at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:30.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さて　始める前に 少しだけ補足しておこう。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:30.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:34.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームは　ソフトそれぞれが 独立してるわけではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:34.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:39.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どのハード機からスタートしても 行き着く先は　皆同じ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:39.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wing scales?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:46.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つのバーチャルエリアに 世界中から 参加できるものと 考えてもらっていい。 プシュ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:46.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The wind is carrying the scales of \Nhis wings toward the citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　メモリーカードを配布する。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その前に順番を決めてもらいたい。 順番？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:59.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームエリアには １人ずつしか入れないのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:59.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They all look completely vacant and dazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:03.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}中で　もめることのないよう ここで順番を決めてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:03.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those scales have a hypnotic effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃ グパジャンで決めようぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Stay in line as you advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし！　１番！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Stay in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:16.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おや？　君は確か… セーブデータを持っていたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:16.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once you reach your position, wait for orders. Do not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:19.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッソ　１７番目かよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:19.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Simple orders delivered repeatedly, \Nwhile tanks roll in the background
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}使うかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}can easily seep into a mind exhausted \Nfrom hours of marching...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:32.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心したまえ。 どのセーブデータでも 最初に行き着く先は　皆同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:32.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the perfect situation for using hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:40.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジン… このゲームは ジンが残したメッセージ 信じて進むよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:40.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once the selection begins, \Nand blood starts to fly, they will continue to quietly stand in place. Until it's their turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:49.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うむ　ならば指輪をはめて ゲームをスタートしたまえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:49.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hypnosis? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン！　俺が行くまで スタート地点で待ってろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they're brainwashed, the citizens won't run. But this works out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we make a lot of noise, we won't have to worry about citizens panicking. Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There won't be any stampede of humans \Nfalling over each other to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:11.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「Ｎｏｗ　Ｐｌａｙｉｎｇ」の文字が出たら 次の者がスタートだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:11.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's a big boon. Assuming that over half of the people \Nwill be in place at midnight, we would have expected a stampede to \Nleave tens of thousands of casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our biggest concern has been addressed. We can go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』へ　ようこそ ゴン＝フリークス様ですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Six hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:38.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これよりゲームの説明をします お聞きになりますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:38.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Everyone's here. Have you heard from Palm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。 このゲームでは その指輪をはめていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰でも使える魔法が２つあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ブック」と「ゲイン」です。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll keep waiting until half \Nan hour before go time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは指輪をはめた手を 前に出し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we knew what's inside before \Ngoing in, it'd be very different...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ブック」と唱えてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブック。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They both look composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームは　指定されたカードを 集めるゲームです。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua, in particular, shows none of the mental weakness he \Ndisplayed when we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは集めたカードを 収める本になります。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd almost say he's brimming with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:11.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初のページを 開いてみてください。 それぞれのポケットに 番号がふってあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:11.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But for some reason, he seems on the verge of fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:18.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのポケットには　同じ番号の カードしか入れることができません。 これを「指定ポケット」といいます。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:18.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I don't have time to worry about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:23.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ページを どんどん　めくってください。 あっ！　番号がない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:23.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm the one suffering from the most anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:28.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　そのポケットには どんな番号のカードも 入れることができます。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:28.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The fate of humanity rests on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを 「フリーポケット」といいます。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Colt is a good guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:35.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}指定ポケットは　ナンバー０から ナンバー９９まで １００個あります。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:35.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meleoron and Ikalgo both have good hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに対し フリーポケットは４５個です。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It doesn't matter if they're humans or Ants. \NEveryone has a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}指定ポケットに入る１００枚の カードをコンプリートすること。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what I want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:47.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが　このゲームの クリア条件となります。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:47.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hopefully, the King also has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１００枚のカードを 集めればいいんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But some of them must be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうです　厳密に言うと １００個のアイテムを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we don't kill them, we'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:58.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カード化して　その本にそろえる ということです。 カード化？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:58.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kite, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}例えば　剣というアイテムを 入手した場合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I promise to turn you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:07.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは手にした瞬間に カードに変わります。 逆に　カードをアイテムとして 使いたい場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:07.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}By defeating that Ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ゲイン」という魔法を使います。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's fired up... I'll focus on providing support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:15.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ゲイン」…。 ただし　一度「ゲイン」で アイテムに戻したら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:15.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So no one can interfere in your battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}二度とカード化されませんので ご注意ください。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Using my new Kanmuru technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}再びカード化したい場合は 再度　入手する必要があります。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここまで　よろしいですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm suffering from days without rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん…　何とか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}On a scale of 1 to 100, my current \Ncondition would be 40...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これ以外にも２つ カード化できないケースがあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, 35...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つは　そのアイテムの カード化限度枚数が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I can't be whining now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マックスになっている場合です。 「カード化限度枚数」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}With Knov out, I'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:45.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　このゲーム内に存在する アイテムには 全て カード化限度枚数があります。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:45.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was hoping to fight at full strength, but it's easier to accept my fate this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:54.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}例えば　カード化限度枚数が ３のアイテムの場合 そのアイテムを　３人のプレーヤーが それぞれカード化してしまったら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:54.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll focus on playing the decoy and \Ndrawing my target from the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たとえ４人目が そのアイテムを手に入れても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sorry, Morel and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードにできないということです。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I can't bring myself to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　もう１つ！ え？ カードは 本に入れずに１分経つと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll take a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:16.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この場合も 二度とカード化はできません。 お分かりになりましたか？ うん…　何とか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:16.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So two minutes is the longest \NI can hold my breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最後に　最も重要な注意点。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Given how tense I'll be inside, my limit \Nwill probably be, at most, half that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}う…　そろそろ覚えきれないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしも　プレーヤーが 死んでしまった場合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One minute is more than enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本と指輪は破壊され 中のカードは全て消滅します。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tomorrow, at midnight, I will be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死んじゃったら そんなの関係ないと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A few days ago, I couldn't have \Ndreamed of such a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}以上で説明は終わりです あとはゲームを進めながら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thank you, Killua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}より詳しい情報を ご自分で入手してください。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I promise to carry out my mission for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　分かった　ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tomorrow will be my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジン!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:12.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは　俺が仲間と作ったゲームだ 楽しんで行ってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:12.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:23.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　俺の元へ　たどり着く 手掛かりがあると思ったら あいにくだったな。 俺は　ただ　このゲームを 自慢したいだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:23.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why was I brought into this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:30.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理由が　どうであれ ここまで来た以上 あるアイテムを手に入れない限り ここから出られない。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:30.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Time's up... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』に 足を踏み入れたゴン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Palm...
